0.text: Bug 8595  'Open super implementation' should be disabled.

1.text: In the Outline view, there seems to be a new menu item 'Open super  implementation', and a corresponding decoration on methods to indicate thet  they have a super implementation.

2.text: The UI already knows if the method has a super implementation, so it should  disable the menu item when there is no super implementation to open to.

3.text: Currently it just does nothing if you select a method with no super  implementation.
